How long do I know you, Chuck?

50
00:04:19,301 --> 00:04:21,553
哦，胖了9年，10年。
Oh, a fat nine, ten years.

51
00:04:21,678 --> 00:04:26,641
我们第一次见面时，你谈的都是新协议，公平协议之类的。
When we first met, all you could talk about was the new deal or the fair deal or some deal.

52
00:04:27,100 --> 00:04:31,271
