Ibehevedinit what do you believe in now?

53
00:04:31,396 --> 00:04:37,235
健康，努力工作，生的烤牛肉和好的剧本。
Health, hard work, rare roast beef and good scripts.

54
00:04:37,819 --> 00:04:39,738
你比以前聪明多了。
You're a lot smarter child than you used to be.

55
00:04:39,863 --> 00:04:41,281
我必须学习，帕特丽夏。
I had to learn, Patricia.

56
00:04:41,406 --> 00:04:44,159
查理的口号是:“收到消息，通知西部联合电报公司。”
Charlie's slogan: "Got a message, send for western union."

57
00:04:44,284 --> 00:04:47,746
-我听说你的新电影不错。-它会分红的。
- I hear your new picture's good. - It'll pay a dividend.

58
00:04:47,871 --> 00:04:50,499
-那你的新合同呢?-怎么了，伙计?
- What about your new contract? - What about it, buddy?

59
00:04:50,624 --> 00:04:55,337
电影公司得到了所有的合同…斯坦利·霍夫上周告诉我，你打算续签。
The studio got the contracts all... Stanley hoff told me last week, you were about to re-sign.

60
00:04:55,462 --> 00:04:58,799
他是工作室的负责人。梦想不需要他付出任何代价。
