I don't get your point, sweetie. Buddy went to jail for 10 months.

88
00:06:33,768 --> 00:06:35,896
再说，这都是过去的事了。
Besides, it's all past and forgotten.

89
00:06:36,021 --> 00:06:38,565
如果我选择复活它，它不会被遗忘。
It's not forgotten if I choose to revive it.

90
00:06:38,690 --> 00:06:40,609
