Now, why would you want to do that?

91
00:06:40,734 --> 00:06:43,904
你们有些人忘记了这个城市必须保持干净。
Some of you forget that this town has got to keep its skirts clean.

92
00:06:44,029 --> 00:06:51,828
在摄影棚的圣诞派对上，这个白痴偷了你的车…-他借了我的车。-他半醉半醒地开车…他没有喝醉，亲爱的。这在法庭上被澄清了。
At the studio Christmas party, this idiot steals your car... - He borrowed my car. - He drives along half-drunk... He wasn't drunk, sweetie. That was cleared in court.

93
00:06:51,953 --> 00:06:53,830
