- All he did... - Now, Patty.

96
00:07:01,588 --> 00:07:06,384
他所做的一切，你亲爱的朋友，几乎毁了我的职业生涯。
All he did, your dear friend, was to almost ruin a career right out of the storybooks.

97
00:07:06,509 --> 00:07:09,137
我以为我们能像个正常人一样原谅他。
I thought we could be human enough to forgive that.

98
00:07:09,262 --> 00:07:11,848
难道他没有及时站出来承担责任吗?
Didn't he step up in time and take the blame?

99
00:07:12,641 --> 00:07:17,812
我还是觉得让他重回工作岗位是非常糟糕的公共关系。
Well, I still think it was very poor public relations giving him his job back that way.

100
00:07:17,938 --> 00:07:26,655
